text: The Lainong tribe (also known as Htang Ngan, Leinong) is one of the Naga tribes that mostly resides in Naga Self-Administered Zone in Myanmar . They are one of the major Naga tribes of Myanmar and mostly inhabits around Lahe Township in Myanmar. ==References== Category:Naga people Category:Ethnic groups in Myanmar
title: Lainong Naga
